## Verification

```bash
# Guide no longer contains stale "published" filter
grep -q '"published"' WAI-Spoke/WAI-Guide.md && echo "FAIL — stale filter still present" || echo "PASS — filter clean"

# Guide no longer references WAI-Signals.jsonl
grep -q "WAI-Signals.jsonl" WAI-Spoke/WAI-Guide.md && echo "FAIL — stale ref still present" || echo "PASS — clean"
```

